# Auth

## Flow

1. Login / Register submit → `sendOtp()` → navigate to `/verify-otp`
2. OTP verify → login sets user; register creates org with role **`owner`** (Organization Owner)
3. Forgot password → `/verify-email` (separate from OTP flow)

## Files

- Mock auth logic: `src/lib/auth.ts`
- Email normalize / OTP / delay: import from `src/lib/helper.ts`
- Auth preview mock data: `src/data/auth-previews.ts` (not inline in preview components)
- Reusable auth UI: `auth-form-layout.tsx`, `auth-form-card.tsx`, `auth-page-shell.tsx`

## UI

- Split layout for login/register; centered shell for forgot/verify pages
- Use `ConfirmModal` pattern only where confirmation is needed (admin logout, not login submit)
